data.description:
Back on the market, no fault of the seller. Welcome to your dream home! This  3-bedroom residence, boasting an additional non-conforming 4th bedroom in the basement, offers unparalleled comfort and versatility. With 3 full bathrooms, two spacious living rooms, an entertainment area in the basement, and a convenient 2-car garage, this property is designed for modern living and entertaining.

The primary suite is a true retreat with an ensuite bathroom and ample closet space. Two additional bedrooms on the main level provide flexibility for a growing family, home office, or guest accommodations.

The lower level surprises with a non-conforming 4th bedroom, offering privacy and versatility for various needs. This additional space could be a home office, gym, or a cozy guest retreat. You also have another living room that could be perfect as a play area. A full bathroom on this level adds to the convenience and functionality of this unique home.

The property's charm extends outdoors, where a  yard provides a serene backdrop for relaxation and play. The 2-car garage ensures your vehicles are protected from the elements, adding an extra layer of convenience.

Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is within proximity to schools, parks, highways, and shopping, ensuring that all your daily needs are easily met. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own - schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect blend of style, space, and functionality!
